# About scDrugHunter

**scDrugHunter** evaluate potential gene-drug interactions associated with candidate genes by single-cell gene expression specificity level in each cell type,  correlation between single-cell gene expression and phenotypes, significance of eQTL-phenotype associations and the drug-gene interaction score provided by DGIdb database

## Installation

You can install the released version of scPagwas from [github](https://github.com/x-burner-ux/scDrugHunter) with:

```r
#install some dependence packages
install.packages("circlize")
if (!require("BiocManager", quietly = TRUE))
    install.packages("BiocManager")
BiocManager::install("ggradar")

devtools::install_github("x-burner-ux/scDrugHunter")
```

## Tutorials

scDrugHunter provides a tutorial [Quik_start_for_scDrugHunter]() with quick example. Please also visit the documentation.
